Using the :zephyr:ref:`Display driver API <display_api>` with chosen
display. That is:

| :hwftlbl-scr:`LCD` : :dts:`chosen { zephyr,display = &lcd_panel; };`
| :hwftlbl-scr:`ST7796S` : :dts:`lcd_panel: &st7796s_480x320 {};`

